  "original_title": "\u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0db1 \u0db4\u0ddd\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dcf\u0db8\u0d82\u0d9a\u0da9 \u0dc0\u0dd0\u0dc4\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel queues block sidewalks",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The I.O.C. located at Pamankada Handi. Heavy traffic can be seen in the footpath area due to the parking of vehicles in order to get fuel from the two petrol stations.",
        "There are queues of vehicles on both sides of the road to the two petrol stations and only a section in the middle of the road is left for vehicles driving on both sides.",
        "The people were in a lot of trouble due to the fact that the buses running from that area were stuck in the traffic jams of Route No. 138 and 120."
      ],
